intent.user_query: What are the names and emails of the customers who have open service tickets?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT DISTINCT c.FirstName, c.LastName, c.Email FROM fitness_db.Customers c JOIN fitness_db.ServiceTickets st ON c.CustomerID = st.CustomerID WHERE st.Status <> 'Resolved';

arguments.sql: SELECT DISTINCT c.FirstName, c.LastName, c.Email FROM fitness_db.Customers c JOIN fitness_db.ServiceTickets st ON c.CustomerID = st.CustomerID WHERE st.Status <> 'Resolved';

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
